Labor intensive sectors with the potential to provide digital tools to their workforce.

Labor: the degree to which they put digital tools in the hands of their employees to ramp up productivity.

RPA is the digitization of labor enabled by advancements in machine intelligence, digital,
analytics, cognitive, big data, social, mobile and cloud to replace business process
functions.

The process of the automating the deployment steps using tools.

Managing the multiple applications using the single tool called as application orchestration, to reduce management of applications.
